are my whole world but pregnancy is bitch on your body. I finally feel like I have myself back and I'm so beyond happy about it. 

To any woman struggling with their body after pregnancy, I feel your pain and frustration. It has been a long bumpy road to get to this point. To anyone struggling with their weight, there is always hope. You can do it!

I eat healthy and exercise as much as I can (hard to do while managing two tiny humans) but the main thing I learned through this all is to allow yourself to have cheat days. Eat a damn donut once in a while or big bowl of ice cream and don't hate yourself for it. But most importantly never give up on yourself. 
We all have one life and it is best to make the most of it. Thank you for letting me share this experience with you all!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Y217K3R</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[aticklepickle]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>&quot;Now now baby, mummy's girlboosing&quot;</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PD4d29Q</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VRDbBxD.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PD4d29Q</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Wingsofblows]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Why am I anxious?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/u5Nvvvc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uoJc4ov.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hlGuyjW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFh8WubLzYY

Edit: It was because of my dental appointment today. I figured it out guys.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/u5Nvvvc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Gheebun]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I'm blue da bu dee ...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qa6k43P</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V5QgHOy.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wlowMcf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qa6k43P</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WeirdAlisMySpiritUserName]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I Won Capitalism</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5W6laae</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jO1i9Ks.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#capitalism #funny #billionaire</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5W6laae</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AnToByn]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I'm 39 and I just built first Lego set.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/c5rLgAZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZhAmvHS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I've bought my son tons of sets and they've always looked like it would be really relaxing, so I gave this one a shot. It's really enjoyable and I like that I can swap the cherry blossoms and have it look like a regular bonsai tree.

